# Auth Service

Auth service tự xây dựng (self-hosted), thay thế Zitadel/Supertokens. Nằm trong `app/auth/`.

## Tech Stack

| Thành phần | Công nghệ |
|------------|-----------|
| Framework | Kratos v3 (HTTP 8080 + gRPC 9090) |
| DI | Wire (compile-time) |
| DB | PostgreSQL 18, schema `auth` |
| Cache | Valkey/Redis (session, rate limit, token blacklist) |
| Queue | NATS (outbox pattern) |
| Password | Argon2id (golang.org/x/crypto) |
| JWT | RS256 (golang-jwt/jwt/v5) |
| OAuth2 | golang.org/x/oauth2 + per-provider implementation |
| TOTP | github.com/pquerna/otp (AES-256-GCM encrypted) |
| Migration | goose + sqlc |

